{"type": "article", "id": 15796, "title": "“旅行箱”手提包", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-09T07:35:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135549xXNY2VMghZ7KfGbk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是老佛爷在 2016 春夏时装秀上的展览，将手提包做成迷你版的行李箱。都是长方体的外形配上“拉杆”的样式，侧面的带子、滚轮和四角的保护垫一样都不缺，并适当提亮。有些包用了真皮材质，表面印有 Chanel 经典的菱格纹，在复古的设计中诠释时尚。也许真的成为明年最流行的款式。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143142dFBfqUXSwGcnhRkI.jpg\" width=\"533\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143142ZYLgTwXNRu84pO90.jpg\" width=\"533\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143143hr5E8MJRaGYLiFsK.jpg\" width=\"533\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143144hKADzo9xFVSPwdCO.jpg\" width=\"533\" height=\"800\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}